  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1423499/" class="title-link">称不上是好书，但是不错的文案工具书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1423499"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ciwawa/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1071943-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ciwawa/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">意识流</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-06-29"
      class="main-meta">2008-06-29 11:29:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1423499_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不知道为什么前些年在很多人极力推崇这种后现代风格的文案后，当今一众人又开始大举进攻这一类文字，说是意识形态广告在泛滥，当然这是针对时下的文案们说的，但是对于李欣频，他们想说的是：你太一样了！  我想这正是很多人对这本书的评价并不怎么高的重要原因。但是我也相信...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1423499/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1423499_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1423499_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
